attempts.sparql_query:
PREFIX atm: <http://www.atm.org/ontology#> 
 PREFIX nas: <http://www.nas.org/ontology#> 
 SELECT ?icaoCode 
 WHERE { 
   <http://example.org/AAL1170> atm:departureAirport ?airport . 
   ?airport nas:icaoCode ?icaoCode . 
 }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the ICAO code of the departure airport for flight AAL1170. It first finds the departure airport of the flight using the atm:departureAirport property, and then looks up its ICAO code using the nas:icaoCode property.
